# GRAPHICS::SET_BINK_MOVIE_AUDIO_FRONTEND

## Summary
Control whether or not the audio for the specified bink movie is played frontend (rather than in-world)

## Parameters
* **BINK_MOVIE_ID** movieId
* **BOOL** frontend
